description: Sometimes you just gotta know! This app is built for people with inquisitive minds and insatiable curiosities. Do you dare ask THE question? Give it a go and you won't regret it!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Fourth of July Checker is it the Fourth of July
is it the Fourth of July yet
is today the Fourth of July
name: Fourth of July Checker
shortDescription: Is it the Fourth of July? Is it not the Fourth of July? Enable this skill to find out!
